Laura Aikman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laura_Aikman 0 Laura Holly Aikman (born 24 December 1985) is an English actress and daughter of stunt coordinator and film director Stuart (known professionally as Stuart St. Paul) and Jean. She has been appearing in TV and films since childhood.
